node - server / back end technology

   basic commands 
---------------------
1. create package.json - npm init

2. install express - npm i express 

3. install JWT token - npm insatll jsonwebtoken

    basic steps
---------------------
1. create package. json 

2. install express 

3. create index.js file 

4. import express 

5. server app creation using express 

6. setup port number 

8. response status codes
    1xx - information
    2xx - succes
    3xx - redirection
    4xx - client side error
    5xx - server side error

9. JWT Token - user validation
    9.1 Token generation - sign()
    9.2 Token verify - verify()

10. Middleware - 
    10.1 Application specific
    10.2 Router specific
